General.Name: Orexo AB
General.Description: Orexo AB (publ), a specialty pharmaceutical company, develops and commercializes pharmaceuticals and digital therapies in the United States, European Union, and internationally. Its products include Zubsolv tablets for the treatment of opioid use disorder; Abstral for the treatment of breakthrough pain in cancer patients; and Edluar for the treatment of insomnia. The company is also developing OX124 for opioid overdose; OX125 for rescue medication and opioid overdose; OX640 for emergency treatment of allergic reactions; and OX-MPI for the treatment of endometriosis. In addition, its digital therapies include deprexis for the treatment of depression; vorvida for alcohol management; and modia for opioid use disorder. Orexo AB (publ) was incorporated in 1994 and is headquartered in Uppsala, Sweden.
